# When multiple jobs in a Docker queue download the same artifact, is any caching used, or is it re-downloaded every run?

Launch jobs share no cache. Each launch job runs independently. To share a cache, configure the queue or agent to mount one with Docker arguments in the queue configuration. For specific use cases, you can also mount the W&B artifacts cache as a persistent volume.

